uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.expr

Class CastLongSQLExpression<N extends java.lang.Number>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.expr.CastLongSQLExpression<N>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GroupingSQLValue<java.lang.Long>, SQLExpression<java.lang.Long>, SQLValue<java.lang.Long>, Targetted<java.lang.Long>

    public class CastLongSQLExpression<N extends java.lang.Number>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SQLExpression<java.lang.Long>
    A SQLExpression that interprets a numeric SQLExpression to as a long. This does not alter the SQL expression just the type it is interpretted as.
